title: Screwed my Live Wallpapers and Themes(Normal wallpapers OK)
content:
tried to be too clever and downloaded an apk that I thought had the Pixel 5 Live Wallpapers in but it seems to have overwritten my existing Live wallpapers and my Themes; have lost the original live wallpaper and Pinball. The Pixel 5 Live Wallpapers are there and work. My themes icon is now a bit odd and leads to a black screen if i click on it. Is there any way to recover the original Live wallpaper and Themes for the 4a please? Ordinary wallpapers appear intact.
I know I'm an idiot and promise to behave myself in future...  TIA
